text: Keeping Up with the Kardashians'most reclusive castmember Robert Kardashian tweeted a cute snap of his daughter Dream Renée wading in a swimming pool beside a golf course on Saturday. The 31 - year - old reality star likened his adorable two - year - old princess splashing around to Disney's 2016 Polynesian princess Moana. Upon seeing her swimsuit - clad niece, Rob's big sister Kim retweeted the snap with a heart - eyed emoji.
